name: Package in 1 Minute
description:
A Quick and Simple Game About Delivering Package.

Created for the One Minute Jam.

You Play As a Stickman delivering package to 4 house. grab the packages from the Major and try to get as many package deliver in 1 minute (60 Second).

Control:

Left Arrow : Move Left

Right Arrow : Move Right

X and Space : Jump

Z : to grab the package from the Major
